picam-hailo (1.0.0+202606091437) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial release. Raw YUV420 UDP input from picam-raw replacing RTSP.
  * YOLOv8 NMS output decoding with per-detection JSON output.
  * No FFmpeg dependency — pure HailoRT + POSIX sockets.

